        <div class="discussions-item-body">
            <small class="authorship">

                <a href="/hacker/56227">David Nghiem</a>

                wrote <a class="gray-link" href="/project/4716-control-things-with-your-muscles/discussion-20043">3 months ago</a>

                <span id="comment-points-holder-20043" class="hide">
